    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DLC Special Offer!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324660/extras/2bea2da54ff6c4c61476ef21f89206a6.avif?t=1736216396\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The last gift of 2024! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starting December 24, the Hopeful Chest DLC is available for 14 days at a special price.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can obtain 10 Hopeful Chests when you purchase the DLC.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can receive the following items from the Hopeful Chest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twin Shadow Axes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twin Light Axes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heaven Splitter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Asura Hell Splitter</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324660/extras/4e47994c9e85b42b21a24e3fded9846b.avif?t=1736216396\" width=610 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Notice</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Hopeful Chest is a probability-based product.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The sale ends on 1/6 at 6 PM, PST.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It can be purchased once per account.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This DLC is a non-refundable item, so please purchase it carefully.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Hopeful Chests from the DLC will be removed during 1/22 (Wed) maintenance at the end of the promotion period.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will receive the contents of the removed Hopeful Chests if you had any removed.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 10th Anniversary Box will automatically be sent to your inventory after you purchase the DLC.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't miss this special opportunity!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
